import PyPDF2
from pathlib import Path

pdf_path = Path('/workspace/benchmark/datasets/2-HITs/HierarchyTransformers/paper.pdf')
reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(str(pdf_path))
pages_text = []
for page in reader.pages:
    pages_text.append(page.extract_text())
paper_text = '\n'.join(pages_text)
print(paper_text[:2000])  # Print the first 2000 characters for inspection
